# Terraphim AI - Private File Patterns
# =====================================
# This file lists patterns for files and directories that should NOT be pushed
# to public repositories. These patterns are used by the pre-push hook and
# validation scripts to prevent sensitive data leaks.
#
# Pattern syntax:
# - Use shell glob patterns
# - Lines starting with # are comments
# - Empty lines are ignored
# - Patterns are matched against file paths relative to repository root
#
# DO NOT delete this file - it's essential for security

# Client and Customer Data
# ------------------------
# Note: Exclude legitimate client libraries like terraphim_atomic_client
client-*
!crates/terraphim_atomic_client/
customer-*
customers/
clients/
*-client-*
!*atomic_client*
*-customer-*
proprietary/
confidential/

